== THIS IS EXPERIMENTAL CODE! ==

This is an experimental second-coming of the HtmlForm and QuickTemplate classes.

== General Objective ==

Provide a managed way to generate HTML user interface components.

== Outline of Proposed Functionality ==

Filters (Validation)

* Minimum length
* Maximum length
* Pattern (regex)
* Compare (a [operation] [value|b])

Workflows

* a requires [b, c, d, â€¦]
* a confirms b

Fields

* Text (single-line, multi-line - options/suggestions, auto-grow)
* MultiText (multiple texts with options)
* Opton (radio buttons, dropdown list, slider, knob, etc.)
* MultiOption (multiple checkboxes, multi-select list)
